{"tid":2423994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國暫停進口台灣鳳梨","createTime":"2021-02-26T08:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T17:08:22.000Z","uid":258815,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"24daa42cb2753f1844f8532adb385c3360766f59","tid":2423994,"uid":258815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:59:18.000Z","msg":"（中央社台北26日電）中國海關總署今天發布公告稱，自3月1日起暫停進口台灣的鳳梨。國台辦隨後發出新聞稿表示，因多次從進口鳳梨中驗出有害生物，為從源頭防範植物疫情風險，因此採取這項正常措施。<br />\n<br />\n中國海關總署上午發布公告：「從今年3月1日起，暫停受理台灣鳳梨報關、輸入，並及時通知轄區內的相關企業。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.cna.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.cna.com&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=54ca0c6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.cna.com</a><br />\n<br />\n幾時停埋進口台灣晶圓？"},{"pid":"0fd49ba54dcf7a6e7a6ddf6f030d8f0a166b98f6","tid":2423994,"uid":258815,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:01:23.000Z","msg":"香港邊度買到台灣鳳梨？買黎支持下"},{"pid":"052ed21506da7205ac64d1343b07c07b16f4e372","tid":2423994,"uid":258815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7654130f69bd925529a072495aba4ffb3bf6932c","tid":2423994,"uid":253578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:06:48.000Z","msg":"有咩有害生物係到呀?"},{"pid":"7cd216f1e118ed165e0fddc11e8cadae9c4c1087","tid":2423994,"uid":189573,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"請問樓主咩係晶圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791a973cd64b4f7dbb541776efee4184e3a19519","tid":2423994,"uid":37586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"工